title: 10/29/20 DPS-BEST OF

description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, Dan has some information about Big Ten Football. Could Wisconsin have jeopardized the football season for the entire conference? Will we still see Nebraska play this weekend? We're joined by Houston area Morning drive host Sean Salisbury, Sports Illustrated's Chris Mannix and MLB HoFer Johnny Bench. Plus, when can we expect the NBA to return for a 2020-2021 Season?
